                            Newark, so you know you're dealing with a local
                            business.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Open 7 Days</strong>: We work every day of
                            the week, so we can help you no matter how busy your
                            schedule is.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>24 Hour Fitting</strong>: We specialise in
                            providing an emergency 24 hour tyre fitting service
                            in Newark.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <h2 class="fw-bold">Areas We Cover</h2>
                    <p>
                        We cover a wide range of Newark-on-Trent, including:
                        <a href="/areas/southwell" class="link-danger"
                            >Southwell</a
